data.description:
ADORABLE and AFFORDABLE starter home in a great location! The curb appeal is a warm introduction to a spacious entryway and split floor plan with an open concept main living area. The large island is perfect for cooking and conversations. Your secluded owner suite features an en suite bathroom and walk-in closet. The Low maintenance backyard is perfect for four legged friends and summer fun!


20 minutes or less to many of the Metroplex entertainment options like the Arlington Sports and Entertainment District, home of the World Champion Texas Rangers, Dallas Cowboys, Six Flags and Texas Live! Downtown Fort Worth, The Stockyards, Sundance Square and the Museum District. Downtown Dallas, Trinity Groves and the DFW Airport.

USE THE LINK TO TAKE THE 3D VIRTUAL TOUR!
